data.description: Are you seriously wanting to move to the country near the lake well here it is!  This beautiful home with 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, and Den sets on 2 Acres.  Kitchen is very spacious with abundance of cabinets, island and pantry. Enjoy the huge master bedroom, with master bathroom.  Master bathroom has a soaking tub.  This home has so many updates!  In 2019- New gas lines and propane were added to the house so there would always be heat even when the electric went out! In 2020- New hot water heater, New Roof with Heritage 35 years shingles! In 2021- New Deck was put on the front of the home.  So just imagine setting on the deck and watching the wildlife! Seller says they see deer often!  That is not all there is a super nice detached 20X30 shop!  If you enjoy hunting and fishing, this is the ideal place to be because it is located just a few miles from the access to Oologah lake (Big Creek) and the wildlife management area. This home has been remodeled inside and out!
